de.btu.openinfra.backend.db

Enum OpenInfraOrderByEnum

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OpenInfraOrderByEnum>
      • de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.OpenInfraOrderByEnum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<OpenInfraOrderByEnum>

    public enum OpenInfraOrderByEnum
extends Enum<OpenInfraOrderByEnum>
    This enumeration defines table columns which should be ordered. In addition a list of model classes must be specified that will support this column for sorting. The enum must be written in the same way as the table column name that should be sorted.
    Author:
    BTU DBIS
